            "title": "ADR低水35點   夜期跌30點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股ADR較恆指昨日收市低收35點或0.13%，報26509點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"李寧門店\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20240624_FI_source-bp_02331-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"李寧門店\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20240624_FI_source-bp_02331-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">李寧門店</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">體育用品股高水，李寧(02331)ADR較本港收市價高3.9%%，折合18.45港元 ;安踏(02020)ADR較本港收市價高1.2%，折合97.93港元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR折合港元計收報108.44元，較香港收市價高1.5% ; 友邦保險(01299) ADR收市折合港幣71.83元，平水 ; 港交所(00388) ADR收市折合港幣444.15元，較香港收市價低水0.2%; 中國平安(02318) ADR收市折合港幣53.73元，較香港收市價低0.4% ; 招商銀行(03988) ADR收市折合港幣47.01元，較香港收市價低0.3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">科網股普遍低水， 京東(09618) ADR較港收市價較港收市價低1.7%，報136.39元 ; 阿里巴巴(09988) ADR較港收市價低0.5%，折合158.25港元 ; 騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣640.42元，低水0.3% ; 小米(01810) ADR較香港收市價低0.2%，折合56.56港元 ; 美團(03690) ADR較香港收市價低0.6%，折合105.71元 。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指夜市期指收報26535點，跌30點，較昨日恒指收市26545點，低水10點，成交14866張。國指夜市期指收報9468點，較昨日國指收市低水4點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15276770-adr%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b435%e9%bb%9e-%e5%a4%9c%e6%9c%9f%e8%b7%8c30%e9%bb%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-3.jpg.webp",
