            "title": "油價低收逾1%　連跌3日",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">原油期貨價格跌逾1%，連跌3日，受到石油供應繼續保持強勁，但需求下降影響。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/OILPRICE-1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/OILPRICE-1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約期油收報每桶62.68美元，下跌89美仙，跌幅1.4%。連續第三個交易日下跌，本周累計下跌逾0.01%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">倫敦布蘭特期油收報每桶66.68美元，下跌76美仙，跌幅1.12%，連續第三個交易日走低，本周累跌超0.46%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15276455-%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e4%bd%8e%e6%94%b6%e9%80%be1%e3%80%80%e9%80%a3%e8%b7%8c3%e6%97%a5-3",
